uuid = '00000000-1111-2222-3333-444444444444'
attributes = []
payload = payloads.GetAttributesResponsePayload(unique_identifier=uuid,
    attributes=attributes)
batch_item = ResponseBatchItem(operation=Operation(OperationEnum.
    GET_ATTRIBUTES), response_payload=payload)
result = self.client._process_get_attributes_batch_item(batch_item)
self.assertIsInstance(result, GetAttributesResult)
self.assertEqual(uuid, result.uuid)
self.assertEqual(attributes, result.attributes)
